00:01:12,430 --> 00:01:13,764
DANIEL (in French):
Come, Snoop!

20
00:01:13,848 --> 00:01:15,141
ZOE (in English):
It's troubling to the reader,

21
00:01:15,224 --> 00:01:16,767
