277
00:14:59,131 --> 00:15:00,675
it was nothing special, really.

278
00:15:00,758 --> 00:15:03,511
And, uh...

279
00:15:03,594 --> 00:15:04,971
he...

280
00:15:05,054 --> 00:15:06,973
He went back upstairs
