281
00:15:07,056 --> 00:15:08,516
and I worked a little in bed.

282
00:15:09,559 --> 00:15:10,852
VINCENT:
You wrote?

283
00:15:10,935 --> 00:15:12,436
-On your computer?
-Yes.

284
00:15:12,520 --> 00:15:14,188
I finished a translation.

