286
00:15:16,023 --> 00:15:17,233
it's for extra money.

287
00:15:18,568 --> 00:15:20,444
And, um...

288
00:15:20,528 --> 00:15:22,697
Yeah, I heard him
working upstairs

289
00:15:22,780 --> 00:15:25,366
and play his music for about,

290
00:15:25,449 --> 00:15:28,369
I think, it must have been...
10 minutes.

291
00:15:28,452 --> 00:15:31,664
And then I put some earplugs in,
